<p class="ql-align-center">成都城中度假新晋打卡地来了！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">集吃喝玩乐为一体的「花园城」</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这待一天都不够...</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200810/9e3c893b5000499a87fcd3df6d95a4e6.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">近期</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">miniko在天府新区发现了一个城市花园</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它在小📕书上爆火，大家争相前往打卡</p>
